<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 17:06:22 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>路边绿</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5e558b65dac</link><description>&lt;p&gt;路边绿化&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A plant featuring fragile twigs and small yellow blossoms above street stones. Dreamlike blur effect applied." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a5e558b65dac.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 17:06:22 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>罗斯林地铁站第三长</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5e1a51c84e7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;通往罗斯林地铁站的下行自动扶梯。华盛顿地铁系统中第三长的自动扶梯。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Escalator going down to the Rosslyn metro station. Third longest escalator in the DC metro system." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/teejay/6a5e1a51c84e7.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://teejay.some.pics"&gt;@teejay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:53:49 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>高楼中的教堂</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5e109a257e3</link><description>&lt;p&gt;阿灵顿圣殿联合卫理公会教堂坐落在一个角落，周围是高耸的办公楼和公寓大楼。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Arlington Temple United Methodist Church nestled on a corner among tall office buildings and condominiums." height="2165" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/teejay/6a5e109a257e3.jpg" width="2164"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://teejay.some.pics"&gt;@teejay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:12:13 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5e103109bba</link><description>&lt;p&gt;波托马克河平静的水面上，马里兰州一侧可见MGM的身影，一艘小船缓缓漂过，河近岸则是一个码头。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The calm waters of the Potomac river with the MGM seen on the Maryland side, a small boat drifting past, and a dock on the near side of the river." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/teejay/6a5e103109bba.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://teejay.some.pics"&gt;@teejay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:10:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5e0fb8a9982</link><description>&lt;p&gt;描绘一位深海潜水员看着手中发光球体的壁画。绘于弗吉尼亚州亚历山德里亚市王子街和南帕特里克街交界处一栋白色联排别墅的侧面。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Mural of a deep sea diver looking at a glowing orb in its hands. Painted on the side of a white townhome on the corner of Prince and South Patrick in Alexandria Virginia." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/teejay/6a5e0fb8a9982.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://teejay.some.pics"&gt;@teejay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 12:08:28 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>